DEVELOPMENT:
-----------

        An engine for creating packages is supplied.

        Add an otter package

                cd ottercross

                make \
                otterpacktarg \
                pack=bash \
                version=bash-4.3.30 \
                mirror=https://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/bash/ \
                patch-mirror=https://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/bash/bash-4.3-patches/ \
                keyring=ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/gnu-keyring.gpg \
                sign=bash-4.3.30.tar.gz.sig



        Add an otter library

                cd ottercross

                make \
                createhost \
                pack=pcre \
                version=pcre-8.38 \
                mirror=https://sourceforge.net/projects/pcre/files/pcre/8.38/ \
                patch-mirror=http://www.none.org \
                keyring=ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/gnu-keyring.gpg \
                sign=pcre-8.38.tar.gz.sig


